headline: Here’s L1 Capital International Fund’s Comment on HCA Healthcare (HCA)
summary: L1 Capital, an investment management firm, released its “L1 Capital International Fund” (unhedged) second quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
